OL,3,CLondon City Lionesses signs deal with
OL,4,CAlexia Putellas
OL,6,FFormer Barcelona captain and two-time
OL,7,FBallon d'Or winner Alexia Putellas has
OL,8,Fsigned for London City Lionesses.
OL,10,FSpain international Putellas guided
OL,11,FBarcelona to a fourth Champions League
OL,12,Fcrown in six seasons with victory over
OL,13,FLyon, but had announced she was set to
OL,14,Fbring her 14-year stay at the Spanish
OL,15,Fgiants to an end when her contract
OL,16,Fexpired.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
