OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783772364
OL,3,CLondon City Lionesses signs deal with
OL,4,CAlexia Putellas
OL,6,FThe 32-year-old World Cup winner had
OL,7,Falso been linked with Boston Legacy in
OL,8,Fthe United States, but will now
OL,9,Fcontinue her career in England with
OL,10,Fthe ambitious Lionesses ` who have
OL,11,Falso moved this summer for former
OL,12,FEngland goalkeeper Mary Earps.
OL,14,F"I am thrilled to embark on this new
OL,15,Fchapter with London City Lionesses,"
OL,16,FPutellas said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@dO]
