OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783772364
OL,3,CLondon City Lionesses signs deal with
OL,4,CAlexia Putellas
OL,6,F"The club's ambition and its steadfast
OL,7,Fcommitment to growing as a women-only
OL,8,Findependent club resonate deeply with
OL,9,Fme. I look forward to making an impact
OL,10,Fon the pitch as we challenge for
OL,11,Ftitles.
OL,13,F"Off the pitch, building on my passion
OL,14,Ffor youth development, I am equally
OL,15,Fexcited to work with (owner) Michele
OL,16,F(Kang) in elevating women's football
OL,17,Fin England and on the global stage."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@dO]
