OL,3,CLondon City Lionesses signs deal with
OL,4,CAlexia Putellas
OL,6,FBromley-based London City ` who are
OL,7,Fbacked by American billionaire owner
OL,8,Fand Lyon president Michele Kang `
OL,9,Ffinished sixth in their maiden WSL
OL,10,Fseason and the high-profile addition
OL,11,Fof Putellas will further strengthen
OL,12,Fthe squad.
OL,14,F"Alexia Putellas embodies the pinnacle
OL,15,Fof talent, dedication, and vision in
OL,16,Fwomen's football. Her decision to join
OL,17,Four independent, women-first club is a
OL,18,Fpowerful endorsement of what we are
OL,19,Fbuilding at London City," Kang said on
OL,20,Fthe Lioness' website.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
