OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783772364
OL,3,CLondon City Lionesses signs deal with
OL,4,CAlexia Putellas
OL,6,F"This is more than a signing, it is a
OL,7,Fbold statement about the future of the
OL,8,Fsport.
OL,10,F"Together, we will compete at the
OL,11,Fhighest levels while creating new
OL,12,Fcommercial opportunities and
OL,13,Fdevelopment pathways for the next
OL,14,Fgeneration of female athletes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@_O]
